You can enable bootstrap activity logging using the namespace 'org.grails.plugin.batch'.

For more information about Grails logging, please consult: "Grails Logging":http://grails.org/doc/latest/guide/3.%20Configuration.html#3.1.2%20Logging

{warning}
Be aware that log4j is initialized after some other steps. If you want debug information from Bootstrap before log4j kick in, use @grails.plugins.batch.debugLauncher@ system property.
{warning}
